Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=10}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:01:59.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Este é meu Star Shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:02.48,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,O que há com o corpo desse cara?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:05.52,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele não é mais humano!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:06.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chamas de novo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:08.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Master Nail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:10.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(75,75)}Moon Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.49,0:02:17.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele fica pulando fora!\NNão estamos chegando a lugar nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:22.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece que meus quatro poderes\Nnão servem de muito aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:26.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, mas como ainda não\Ndominei o dedo-pistola,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:28.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,vou ter que usar alguns acessórios!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:31.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza! Essa é minha chance\Nde ir pro próximo vagão!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:33.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, para aí, seu maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:34.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não pode tirar os olhos dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele caiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:41.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Beans Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:46.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que pena...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:48.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu imaginei...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,que você faria algo assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:58.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:01.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Peguei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:04.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu maldito...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ouchie Finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:09.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:11.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele me decifrou...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:14.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Tempest Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa raspou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:18.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele se mexe muito!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:22.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então seu ponto fraco...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,são as costas, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:29.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E posso ver através dos seus truques baratos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:33.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É só questão de tempo até eu vencer, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:35.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se empolgue!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:39.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tenho ponto fraco se fizer {\i1}isso{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:43.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tcharã!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:49.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desiste, sua doninha estúpida?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:52.25,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Como é que se responde a isso...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:57.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas sério, cara, você tem um azar terrível.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você foi e me irritou...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:04.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e calhou de eu estar especialmente {\i1}super{\i0} esta semana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:07.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Diz, amigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:10.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já ouviu falar de um centauro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:16.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O monstro cavalo que é\Nhumano da cintura pra cima?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E daí?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:24.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Con... vert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:41.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não me diga que ele vai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:48.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Centaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:54.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Está ao contrário! Seu corpo vai na frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:05:01.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não critique antes de ver a potência.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Você tem muita cara de pau!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:06.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meus punhos de macarrão sumiram!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:07.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,uma cebola ou algo assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:13.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não adianta continuar lutando.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:16.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aceite sua derrota e me deixe passar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:20.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aceitar minha derrota? Por quê?!\NQuem disse que estou perdendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:25.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sou o Wanze, o ás da CP7!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:29.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Infelizmente pra você, entendo\Na importância dessa missão.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:34.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O governo perseguiu sua companheira,\NNico Robin, por muito tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:37.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é um idiota se acha\Nque eu ia simplesmente deixar você levá-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:41.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ramen Kenpo: Noodle Nail Knocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:54.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Ao preparar uma cebola, primeiro corte\No talo e a raiz sem machucar a polpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:59.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se cortar a fibra de uma vez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,o corte resulta numa superfície impecável e brilhante.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:06.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pare! Fique longe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:07.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ramen Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:13.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}Épluchage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:30.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,V-Você me cortou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah? Eu não fui cortado.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:41.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E se você não colocar amor\Nnas menores tarefas, como descascar,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:44.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,vai estragar o sabor de qualquer prato.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:49.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Facas de cozinha não são espadas.\NNão servem pra cortar pessoas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:52.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas caso não tenha percebido, sua armadura–
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:54.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Kitchen Knife Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:57.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu filho da–
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:06:58.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Œil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:04.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,M-Meus olhos estão afundando!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:05.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixe-os.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:07.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, cale a boca e se renda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu imbecil! Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:18.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não entendo por que diabos vocês\Niam querer resgatar uma mulher dessas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:23.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês não conhecem a verdadeira\Nnatureza da Nico Robin, né?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:25.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquela mulher é...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Nez!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:27.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Joue!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Bouche!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Dents!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:30.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Menton!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:37.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se continuar falando,\Nvou rearranjar seu rosto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:41.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-E-Espera um pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:43.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Sinto que meu rosto encolheu! Para!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:49.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Se você não sabe sobre ela, eu conto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:51.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo sabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:54.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela é uma diaba depravada!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:58.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Parage... Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:15.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,D-D-Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:18.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meu rosto afundou! Espelho! Preciso de um espelho!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:31.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,V-V-Seu desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:35.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,C-Como ousa amassar\Nmeus preciosos olhos e nariz?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é um demônio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:42.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, olha, voltaram ao normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:45.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,V-Verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Senti que voltaram um pouco agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:52.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A-Acho que foi imaginação.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:55.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é culpado de três pecados.
Comment: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:56.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:09:00.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Primeiro, você se disse cozinheiro na minha frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:05.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Segundo, você desrespeitou a comida.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Terceiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:09.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,você insultou nossa amiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:23.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é a definição de "muito latido, pouca mordida".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:30.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, centauro! Essas quatro pernas\Nnão parecem estar ajudando muito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:40.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-E-E-Eu vou cair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:48.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que cena lamentável.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Precisa de ajuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:00.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sua doninha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quase...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quer dar uma mão pra {\i1}mim{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:25.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou indo muito bem, idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:28.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Finalmente peguei você.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:33.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora me diga se ainda acha\Nque minhas quatro patas eram inúteis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca, idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me devolva minhas características!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:45.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Minha amiga está esperando pra ser resgatada\Ndo outro lado daquela porta que você está bloqueando.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:52.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando eu digo que não vou\Ndeixar passar, é sério!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:56.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Backstreet Ramen Kenpo:\NPoison Noodle Cleaver!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:10:58.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Toque nisso e está morto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:01.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, agora, agora, agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:05.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês também não estão\Nsendo enganados por aquela mulher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:07.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela é a pior das piores,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:11.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,uma traidora em série que sobreviveu até\Nagora se escondendo nas sombras!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:13.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o fim da linha pra vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:15.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tomem isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Three-Point...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:20.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Découpage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:07.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele me imobilizou completamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:09.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fui descuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:12.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Descuidado?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpas, desculpas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:27.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Na verdade, por que não aproveita\Nessa chance pra dizer umas últimas palavras, amigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:33.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você não está pensando que vai\Ncontinuar lutando depois disso, está?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:39.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, acho que faz sentido\Njá que ficou desviando de todos os meus ataques.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:46.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você não sabe o quão\Nletais meus socos realmente são.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:50.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ultimate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:34.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, de onde diabos você veio?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acabou com aquele cara do ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:40.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, agora mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:47.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Está ficando barulhento por aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:51.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então os soldados da missão de escolta\Nforam aniquilados, afinal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:53.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nunca foram grande coisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:14:00.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles são os que sequestraram a Robin, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:03.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cuidado. Eles usam artes marciais estranhas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:09.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem é esse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:13.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deve ser o novato da CP9\Nsobre quem o Corgi falava tanto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:17.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se bem me lembro, é um mestre dos quatro poderes\Nchamado Nero ou algo assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:23.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:25.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora vocês vão ver!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:28.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As pessoas me chamam de prodígio da luta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:30.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não me importo mais...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:32.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês são carne morta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:36.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, "novato".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:40.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você... Deve ser o Rob Lucci, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:42.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpe pela apresentação tardia...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um momento, por favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:46.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só preciso matar esse cara, e depois...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:48.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nossas ordens são capturar o Franky vivo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:52.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Colocar seus sentimentos pessoais\Nacima de uma missão é...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, esquece.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:57.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tem três segundos. Comece a correr.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:00.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Três...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:02.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Correr...?! De quem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:04.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dois...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:06.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?! Espera um segundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:07.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você está brincando, né?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:09.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:12.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pare! Você está cometendo um erro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:13.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:32.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma pessoa como você que faz\Ntudo pela metade...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:36.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,não serve pra CP9!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:45.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A menos que tenha dominado todos os seis poderes,\Nvocê não é sobre-humano, garoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:46.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kalifa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:47.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Informe o chefe depois...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:54.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,que o novato era\Nfraco demais pra ser útil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:16:00.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esses caras defendem a justiça?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:02.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Difícil dizer qual lado é o mau, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:10.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acho que não preciso perguntar\Npor que está aqui, intruso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:16.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pelo jeito que abriu aquela porta,\Nnão parece ter muita paciência.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:19.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, acho que não fui bem criado.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se isso é sobre a Nico Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:24.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,desistam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:29.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês estão metendo o nariz\Nem assuntos além de vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:33.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Existem pessoas no mundo que\Nnascem sob estrelas azarentas...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:36.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pessoas que seria melhor\Nmorrerem para o bem de todos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:39.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por exemplo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:45.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,suponha que exista um demônio\Ncapaz de destruir o mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:53.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se quem tem o poder de despertar\Nesse demônio for uma menina inocente de oito anos,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:55.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,vocês não acham...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:17:03.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,que alguém deveria matar aquela\Nmenina pelo bem de todos?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:06.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? Onde quer chegar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:12.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou explicando a situação da Nico Robin pra vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:16.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hoje em dia, ela é uma criminosa completa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:20.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas foi assim que tudo começou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:25.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desde que se lembra,\Na própria existência dela é um pecado.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:29.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela só pode fazer as pessoas\Nfelizes desaparecendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:32.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa é a desgraça que ela carrega.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:39.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essencialmente, ela deveria ter morrido há 20 anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:42.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou verdadeiramente feliz que essa mulher...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:44.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,finalmente será executada.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:45.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:51.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já chega!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:52.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:55.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não ouse dizer mais nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:59.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dito isso, o governo provavelmente\Nvai passar muitos anos...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:10.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,extraindo cada gota do conhecimento, experiência\Ne inteligência da Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:16.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não consigo nem imaginar a agonia que ela vai\Nsuportar de agora até sua morte... Só pense–
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum vamos deixar isso acontecer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.70,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei, espere, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.71,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Você não deveria ir por aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:24.71,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Sério! Sério! Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:28.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, eu disse, espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:32.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:33.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A-Ah, droga...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:36.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Graças a Deus! Você está bem?!\NEstá machucada?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:39.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é muito ruim!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:44.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Já foi difícil entrar pelo lado de fora,\Nmas depois nocautear aquele oficial...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:47.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então essa é a Nico Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:50.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela meio que parece\Ncom a foto do cartaz de procurado.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos voltar juntos dessa vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:19:01.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou derrubar esses caras\Nnum instante... Certo, Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:10.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:11.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que está fazendo, Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:21.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:25.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mesmo se eu explicar,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:27.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,vocês não vão ouvir, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:37.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sr. Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desconecte o vagão três!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que vamos fazer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:43.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Corram!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Correr?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:46.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, como assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:50.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você também, apresse-se!\NUm momento decide tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:52.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não deixem o Franky escapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:53.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:57.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Sogeking...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:20:00.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,192)}Smoke Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que trapaceiro covarde...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:11.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:16.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pegamos a Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:23.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Me coloque no chão!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:27.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Beleza!\N– Beleza!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:30.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Corram!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:41.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Voltem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:43.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por quê?! Viemos até aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:44.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sr. Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:48.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É isso aí! Diga por quê!\N– É isso aí! Diga por quê!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:50.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês não!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:51.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Hã?\N– Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:58.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele sapo idiota pulou nos trilhos!\NVolte, sapinho! Saia do trilho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:01.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o Yokozuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:02.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:06.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,59)}– Que história é essa de sapo gigante?!\N– Que história é essa de sapo gigante?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:10.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sai do caminho, sapo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:15.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(3692,0,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Vamos bater!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:22.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:24.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Recuperamos a Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:26.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, isso foi uma surpresa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:29.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pensar que mudamos pra uma retirada estratégica...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:33.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ninguém esperaria algo\Ntão idiota quanto uma cortina de fumaça.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:41.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É melhor se conseguirmos nosso objetivo\Nsem lutar com caras assustadores como eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:42.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:46.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não sei se as coisas\Nvão ser tão simples.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:51.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É. Não baixem a guarda\Naté os vagões estarem bem longe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:56.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que diabos...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:01.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chicotes espinhosos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:05.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Peguei...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:07.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Blueno.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.64,0:22:08.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:11.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele vai atravessar usando os chicotes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:21.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles nos puxaram de volta!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:23.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele poder é insano!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.08,0:22:29.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma cortina de fumaça? Que truque inútil...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:33.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acho que foi bom demais pra ser verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:40.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os Piratas do Chapéu de Palha devem ser mantidos vivos.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.21,0:22:43.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse foi o acordo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:45.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sogeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.01,0:22:45.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.93,0:22:47.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Proteja a Robin! Entendeu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:49.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã...? É!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:51.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, mas vou...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.56,0:22:53.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,fazer você soltar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:00.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que o corpo dele é tão duro?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:03.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não disse que eles usam artes marciais estranhas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.54,0:23:12.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Concassé!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.26,0:23:24.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os chutes daquele garoto não são brincadeira.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:26.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele quase quebrou o corpo de ferro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:29.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Blueno, não o subestime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:33.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pode não ter recompensa,\Nmas é um dos pesos-pesados deles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:35.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau, R-Robin! E-Ei, e-espera um pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:38.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai... O-O que está fazendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.65,0:23:40.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ocho Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:41.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Clutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:43.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Narigudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.70,0:23:50.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! O que está fazendo, Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.87,0:23:56.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quantas vezes tenho que\Ndizer?! Me deixem em paz!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.96,0:24:03.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.34,0:24:05.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, fiquem atentos.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.60,0:24:15.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sobrancelha!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.02,0:24:20.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pelo amor... Por que\Nvocês todos são tão teimosos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.52,0:24:24.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês são amigos, não são?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.61,0:24:27.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa é...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.07,0:24:33.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,a chance perfeita pra fugir, não?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.41,0:25:11.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.16,0:25:17.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso foi desnecessário.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.91,0:25:21.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não esperava isso, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.50,0:25:26.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que você está do lado\Ndeles, pra começo de conversa?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.46,0:25:28.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não aguento vê-los agir assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.59,0:25:32.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não quando tem uma equipe que não consegue\Nse reunir mesmo querendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.30,0:25:36.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabe de quem você está falando.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.14,0:25:39.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês, não se preocupem comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.77,0:25:41.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho um plano!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.14,0:25:44.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando se juntarem ao Chapéu de Palha,\Nvoltem pra cidade de algum jeito!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.11,0:25:46.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.02,0:25:47.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.36,0:25:49.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não vou fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.07,0:25:52.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espere, Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.91,0:25:55.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que você continua agindo assim?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.24,0:26:00.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Viemos te resgatar sabendo de toda a história!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.71,0:26:05.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se pudermos fazer algo sobre\No buster call do governo,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.79,0:26:09.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,então você não teria motivo\Npra obedecê-los, certo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.26,0:26:19.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse buster call...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.11,0:26:27.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,é exatamente o problema.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.45,0:26:33.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Tempest Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.40,0:26:34.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.54,0:26:39.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.29,0:26:46.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.71,0:26:49.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele apareceu do nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.72,0:26:55.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Blueno desapareceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.22,0:26:57.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele não desapareceu.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.89,0:27:03.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Ele usou a "Porta do Ar"—o poder que faz\Nsua Fruta Porta-Porta valer alguma coisa—
Comment: 0,0:26:57.89,0:26:59.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,He only made a door out of the wall of air by using "Air Door,"
Comment: 0,0:27:00.18,0:27:03.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,He only made a door out of the wall of air by using "Air Door,"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.48,0:27:06.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,pra criar uma porta no próprio ar.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.60,0:27:09.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês não podem escapar de nós...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.57,0:27:11.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Simplesmente não é possível.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.08,0:27:26.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Solte a Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.79,0:27:28.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,ag–
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.42,0:27:32.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Finger Pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.89,0:27:41.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.76,0:27:43.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Iron Body.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.35,0:27:48.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Está sentindo aquele ataque de antes?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.86,0:27:50.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele chute foi risível.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.91,0:28:06.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que teimoso.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.50,0:28:07.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parem!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.04,0:28:12.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não vou fugir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.92,0:28:14.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso já deveria ser suficiente.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.34,0:28:17.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São eles que continuam me atacando.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.51,0:28:19.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não posso evitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.43,0:28:23.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então vamos logo e vamos embora.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.94,0:28:28.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.86,0:28:35.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.11,0:28:36.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin...!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.61,0:28:40.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai... ficar tudo... bem...!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.12,0:28:45.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você... ainda está escondendo algo, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.00,0:28:52.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.38,0:28:54.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.80,0:28:55.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,um pirata...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.26,0:29:00.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,não pode sair da tripulação...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.84,0:29:04.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,sem a permissão...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.14,0:29:05.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,do capitão.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.06,0:29:10.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.19,0:29:12.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,apenas...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.23,0:29:15.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,acredite no Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.96,0:29:36.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espere, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.13,0:29:40.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não adianta. A Nico Robin\Nnão vai quebrar o acordo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.47,0:29:42.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como pode dizer isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.01,0:29:46.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Muitos anos atrás, uma ilha\Nfoi varrida do mapa.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.93,0:29:53.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Foi queimada até os alicerces\Nsem deixar rastro por um buster call...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.02,0:29:55.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,por ordem da Marinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.73,0:30:01.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A única sobrevivente daquele incidente\Nfoi uma garotinha chamada Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.45,0:30:02.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.36,0:30:07.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cinco vice-almirantes e dez navios de guerra...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.33,0:30:11.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Para aquela menina que testemunhou\Ntal poder militar esmagador,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.91,0:30:15.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,o buster call é um pesadelo inextinguível.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.42,0:30:20.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Com aquele horror da infância\Nagora voltado contra seus amigos...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.34,0:30:24.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,ela não tem mais vontade de nos resistir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.22,0:30:26.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não me diga...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.22,0:30:29.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,que vocês sabiam disso desde o início...?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.89,0:30:32.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É claro.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.90,0:30:38.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seus monstros...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.23,0:30:42.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quão depravados vocês monstros {\i1}são{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.82,0:30:45.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tudo o que fazemos é pela justiça.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.47,0:30:48.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenho profunda compaixão por aquela mulher.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.74,0:30:51.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não me venha com essa!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.81,0:31:15.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seus malditos!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.81,0:31:19.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aqui é o Departamento de Gestão de Enies Lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.61,0:31:21.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Está tudo em ordem?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.28,0:31:26.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, estamos trazendo os dois\Ncriminosos dentro do prazo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.20,0:31:30.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A ilha está à vista,\Nentão devemos chegar em breve.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.54,0:31:31.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.79,0:31:34.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bom, estaremos aguardando o retorno de vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.54,0:31:39.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Depois de cinco anos fora, sinto uma verdadeira nostalgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.96,0:31:42.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A ilha sem noite, Enies Lobby.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=11}===============================DIALOGUE============================
